RESEARCH ALERT - Amway Japan downgraded . Merrill Lynch Inc & Co said Tuesday it lowered both its intermediate and long - term rating on the shares of Amway Japan Ltd to accumulate from buy . - - Further details were not immediately available . - - Amway Japan , which markets detergents and cosmetics , revised its 1996 / 1997 group net forecast to 23 . 40 billion yen from 26 . 20 billion yen . - - In Tokyo , the stock closed at 4240 yen . ( Wall Street desk 212 - 859 - 1730 ) ) 
